These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour, climbing, cycling, ice-hockey, basketball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is climbing##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Sport   | rugby | climbing | ice-hockey | water-polo | cycling | parkour | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, goat, goldfish, lizard, rat, horse
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the snake##2
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Pet   | rat | horse | snake | goat | goldfish | hedgehog | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, turtle, goldfish, hamster, rabbit, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | rabbit | hamster | mouse | bird | turtle | goldfish |

