.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, skiing, soccer, snowboarding, cycling, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Sport   | cycling | rowing | soccer | surfing | snowboarding | skateboarding | skiing |

