.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, yellow, pink, amber, azure, light-blue, red
1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes red##1
3. the person who likes amber is the person who likes amber##1
4. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes red and the person who likes amber##2
5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Color   | light-blue | turquise | pink | red | azure | amber | yellow |

