2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching action movies##2
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |   3    |   4    |   5    |   6    |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action | martial-arts | thriller | family | satire | mystery |

